				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I just did a few quick searches on Saryrn in the bazaar. Limiting prices to 100pp for each slot here's what I came up with:
<br />

<br />
Item                                <span style="font-style: italic">Price</span>       <span style="font-weight: bold"> AC</span>
<br />
Netherbian Chitin:             <span style="font-style: italic">5pp</span>          <span style="font-weight: bold">20</span>
<br />
Lightcrawler Vambracers: <span style="font-style: italic">50pp</span>         <span style="font-weight: bold">11</span>
<br />
Spider Fur Cloak:             <span style="font-style: italic">80pp</span>         <span style="font-weight: bold">10</span>
<br />
Orc Fang Earring:             <span style="font-style: italic">50pp(ea)</span>    <span style="font-weight: bold">3</span>
<br />
Crafted Plate Boots:         <span style="font-style: italic">90pp</span>         <span style="font-weight: bold">12</span>
<br />
Jagged Band:                   <span style="font-style: italic">10pp(ea)</span>    <span style="font-weight: bold">5</span>
<br />
Gothic Steel Gauntlets:      <span style="font-style: italic">90pp</span>        <span style="font-weight: bold">13</span>
<br />
Calcified Steel Helmet:     <span style="font-style: italic">100pp</span>        <span style="font-weight: bold">15</span>
<br />
Blackened Alloy Legplates:  <span style="font-style: italic">8pp </span>        <span style="font-weight: bold">11</span>
<br />
Drolvarg Mantle <span style="font-style: italic">10pp</span> <span style="font-weight: bold">7</span>
<br />
Glimmering Mithiril Torque <span style="font-style: italic">75pp</span> <span style="font-weight: bold">15</span>
<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">Gothic Steel Bracer:          <span style="font-style: italic">75pp</span>         <span style="font-weight: bold">11</span></span>
<br />
Total:                               <span style="font-style: italic">653pp </span>      <span style="font-weight: bold">141</span>
<br />

<br />
Compare that with what we can summon (at level 65).
<br />

<br />
Item <span style="font-weight: bold">AC </span> <span style="font-style: italic">Increase(decrease) from bazaar AC</span>
<br />
Breastplate <span style="font-weight: bold">17 </span> <span style="font-style: italic">(3)</span>
<br />
Arms <span style="font-weight: bold">8</span> <span style="font-style: italic">(3)</span>
<br />
Elemental Defender/Back <span style="font-weight: bold">10 </span>0
<br />
Earrings <span style="font-weight: bold">6</span> <span style="font-style: italic">3(each)</span>
<br />
Boots <span style="font-weight: bold">8</span> <span style="font-style: italic">(4)</span>
<br />
Rings <span style="font-weight: bold">6</span> <span style="font-style: italic">1(each)</span>
<br />
Gauntlets <span style="font-weight: bold">9</span> <span style="font-style: italic">(4)</span>
<br />
Helmet <span style="font-weight: bold">10 </span> <span style="font-style: italic">(5)</span>
<br />
Legs <span style="font-weight: bold">10 </span> <span style="font-style: italic">(1)</span>
<br />
Bracers <span style="font-weight: bold">8</span>  <span style="font-style: italic">(3)(each)</span>
<br />
Neck <span style="font-weight: bold">8</span> <span style="font-style: italic">1</span>
<br />
Shoulders <span style="font-weight: bold">9</span> <span style="font-style: italic">(6)</span>
<br />
Total <span style="font-weight: bold">135</span> <span style="font-style: italic">(6)</span>
<br />

<br />
So with a budget of 653pp (give or take a bit, depending on your server's economy) you will get a net AC increase of 6 if you head to the bazaar. If you do the mix and match of buying stuff that increases your pet's ac over summoned gear and maximize that with the cheap stuff in the bazaar (netherbian chitin for Saryrn) it might help but that imo is more of a hassle than it's worth.
<br />

