			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">For those considering this route, a couple things to think about.
<br />

<br />
* Pets, being NPCs, may not be on the same "tables" as PCs.
<br />

<br />
* PCs need increments of 100 AC to show any change in mitigation.
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">c.f., </span><a href="http://www.thesteelwarrior.org/forum/showthread.php?s=&threadid=13" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://www.thesteelwarrior.org/forum/showthread.php?s=&threadid=13</a><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.sovereignguild.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4429" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Itchyban of Veeshan</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
